# Normalize line endings to LF for all text files so formatting/lint is
# consistent across Windows and the Linux CI runners.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Lockfiles and generated assets — treat as text, LF, but skip diffs.
pnpm-lock.yaml linguist-generated=true -diff

# Binary assets
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.webp binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
